          <text>
                    <body>
                              <pb n="1"/>
                              <p rend="align(right)">
                                        <placeName>Norwich Muskingum Co Ohio</placeName>
                                        <date>Feb 17.'53</date>
                              </p>
                              <p>
                                        <addressee>Rev. Isaac Leeser</addressee>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="indent(2)">Dear Sir,</p>
                              <p rend="indent(3)">As my property is removed<lb/> from <placeName>New
                                                  York</placeName>, I hope you will no longer<lb/>
                                        send my Occident there, and as I now reside<lb/> with my
                                        father and read his Occident I hope<lb/> you will keep my
                                        Nos. until I send you other<lb/> word. My residence here I
                                        consider only temporary<lb/> and when I get another location
                                        I will have you<lb/> send all my back Nos. thither. If you
                                        have sent<lb/> none to <placeName>New York</placeName> since
                                        I left there, so much the<lb/> better. You will continue to
                                        send to my father, and<lb/> if I can get you other
                                        subscribers, as I think<lb/> probably I can, I will do so. I
                                        suppose you will<lb/> still continue to conduct it with
                                        former liberality.<lb/>
                                        <persName>Mr. Steins</persName> Occident you will
                                        discontinue, unless he<lb/> otherwise directs. We have not
                                        received any Nos since<lb/>
                                        <date>December</date>, and I hope soon to be highly
                                        entertained<lb/> with an account of your western tour and
                                        the<lb/> information which you have collected.</p>
                              <p rend="indent(6)">Yours most respectfully</p>
                              <p rend="indent(8)">
                                        <persName role="author">M. R. Miller</persName>
                              </p>
